name: Moff Gideon
quoteHint: You see, every society has something to offer. The cloners. The Jedi. And even the Mandalorians. By aggregating the best of each, I will create an army that will bring order to the galaxy.
masterHint: Imperial officer who led a faction of remaining Imperial soldiers after the battle of Endor. He had a goal to capture Grogu.

name: Iden Versio
quoteHint: We fight so that others can live. And if we die, it better be for the same reason.
masterHint: Imperial TIE fighter pilot who became the Commander of Inferno Squad. She later defected to support the New Republic.

name: Mas Amedda
quoteHint: The Senate must vote the chancellor emergency powers. He can then approve the creation of an army.
masterHint: Trusted political servant of Supreme Chancellor (and later Emperor) Palpatine.

name: Luminara Unduli
quoteHint: We suffer a great many losses in these battles. Too many.
masterHint: Jedi Master who was executed by the Empire. Her remains were used to lure surviving Jedi to their deaths.

name: Boss Nass (Rugor Nass)
quoteHint: Mesa lika this. Maybe wesa being friends.
masterHint: Leader of the Gungans who established relations between the Gungan people and the humans on Naboo's surface.

name: Admiral Trench
quoteHint: I smell fear, and it smells good.
masterHint: Brilliant cyborg tactician for the Separatist forces. Killed by Anakin Skywalker during the Clone Wars.

name: Bodhi Rook
quoteHint: Would I risk everything for a lie? We don’t have time for this!
masterHint: Former Imperial pilot who defected to join the Rebel Alliance. He helped with stealing the Death Star plans on Scarif.

name: Chopper (C1-10P)
quoteHint: *Beep beep beeeep*
masterHint: Trusted astromech companion to Hera Syndulla.

name: Tech (CT-9902)
quoteHint: I may process moments and thoughts differently, but it does not mean that I feel any less than you.
masterHint: Genetically mutated clone whose mastery of technology allowed him to serve in Clone Force 99.

name: Wrecker (CT-9903)
quoteHint: Why don't you pick on someone not your size?
masterHint: Well-meaning, incredibly strong, but not very intelligent clone. He served in Clone Force 99. His left eye is blind.

name: Sergeant Hunter (CT-9901)
quoteHint: Blind allegiance makes you a pawn. A real leader protects his squad.
masterHint: Leader of a clone special forces squad that largely defected after the formation of the Empire.

name: Carasynthia Dune (Cara Dune)
quoteHint: We were peacekeepers, protecting delegates, suppressing riots. Not what I signed up for.
masterHint: Companion to Din Djarin and Grogu. Was previously a New Republic shock trooper.

name: Ninety-Nine (99)
quoteHint: I'm a soldier, like you. This is what I was bred for.
masterHint: Maintenance clone who was rendered genetically defective during his cloning process. He died during the invasion of Kamino.

name: Jabba The Hutt (Jabba Tiure)
quoteHint: Jedi mind tricks don't work on me. Only money.
masterHint: Notorious crime lord in the outer rim. Has a palace on Tatooine.

name: Qi'ra
quoteHint: It's not that kind of game, Han. The object isn't to win. It's just to stay in it as long as you can.
masterHint: Skilled criminal and lover and partner of Han Solo. Worked for Maul in Crimson Dawn.

name: Baze Malbus
quoteHint: Can you get down from here alone or should I throw you?
masterHint: Companion to Chirrut Imwe. Joined forces with Jyn Erso and the Rebels to steal the Death Start plans on Scarif.

name: Chirrut Imwe
quoteHint: I'm one with the Force; the Force is with me.
masterHint: Having lost his vision, he relies on the Force to see. He was part of the team to steal the Death Start plans on Scarif.

name: The Stranger
quoteHint: I have no name. But the Jedi like you might call me… Sith.
masterHint: A Sith Lord who was trained by Darth Plagueis during the High Republic era. He eventually tried to take on his own apprentice.

name: Garazeb Orrelios (Zeb)
quoteHint: There's just something about the feeling of their helmets on my fists.
masterHint: Very large member of the The Ghost. Friend to Ezra Bridger and the rest of the crew.

name: Dexter Jettster
quoteHint: I should think that you Jedi would have more respect for the difference between knowledge and wisdom.
masterHint: Owner of a Coruscant diner and unlikely friend of Obi-Wan Kenobi.

name: Beru Whitesun Lars
quoteHint: Luke's just not a farmer, Owen. He has too much of his father in him.
masterHint: Adoptive caretaker of Luke Skywalker. She died during an Imperial raid on her home.

name: Satele Shan
quoteHint: These are the moments we strive for, when the hope of victory becomes real. When we can see peace on the horizon.
masterHint: Grand Master of the Jedi Order on Coruscant during the Old Republic era. She is the direct descendent of another famous Jedi of that time.

name: Darth Malgus (Veradun)
quoteHint: I have done what so many Sith pretend to do, but never really achieve… I have broken my chains.
masterHint: Sith Lord and ruler of the Sith Empire during the reign of the Old Republic. Sacked the Jedi Temple on Corsucant.

name: Carth Onasi
quoteHint: Warriors attack and conquer, they prey on the weak. Soldiers defend and protect the innocent—mostly from warriors.
masterHint: Jaded pilot for the Republic who lost his family during the destruction of Telos by the Sith Empire.

name: Darth Malak (Alek)
quoteHint: If we pass beyond this door, we can never go back. The Order will surely banish us. Are the secrets of the Star Forge so valuable?
masterHint: Former apprentice to Darth Revan and leader of the Sith Empire.

name: Luke Skywalker
quoteHint: I am a Jedi, like my father before me.
masterHint: Farm boy from Tatooine who became the last Jedi Knight, destroyed the Death Star, and redeemed his father Darth Vader.

name: Leia Organa
quoteHint: Aren't you a little short for a stormtrooper?
masterHint: Princess and senator from Alderaan, leader of the Rebel Alliance.

name: Darth Vader
quoteHint: Most impressive.
masterHint: Dark Lord of the Sith, former Jedi Anakin Skywalker, fell to the dark side and served the Emperor until his redemption.

name: Han Solo
quoteHint: Never tell me the odds!
masterHint: Smuggler and captain of the Millennium Falcon who became a hero of the Rebellion and married Princess Leia.

name: Yoda
quoteHint: If once you start down the dark path, forever will it dominate your destiny. Consume you it will.
masterHint: Ancient and wise Jedi Master who trained Jedi for 800 years, including Luke Skywalker and Count Dooku.

name: Obi-Wan Kenobi
quoteHint: Oh I'm not brave enough for politics.
masterHint: Jedi Master who trained Anakin Skywalker and later watched over Luke on Tatooine.

name: Chewbacca
quoteHint: *Roar*
masterHint: Loyal Wookiee co-pilot of the Millennium Falcon.

name: R2-D2
quoteHint: *Beep boop beep*
masterHint: Brave astromech droid who served Padmé Amidala, Anakin Skywalker, and later Luke Skywalker through multiple conflicts.

name: C-3PO
quoteHint: We're doomed!
masterHint: Protocol droid fluent in over six million forms of communication, built by Anakin Skywalker.

name: Padme Amidala
quoteHint: So this is how liberty dies... with thunderous applause.
masterHint: Queen and Senator of Naboo.

name: Anakin Skywalker
quoteHint: I don't like sand. It's coarse and rough and irritating, and it gets everywhere.
masterHint: Jedi Knight known as the Chosen One who fell to the dark side and became Darth Vader, father of Luke and Leia.

name: Mace Windu
quoteHint: This party's over.
masterHint: Senior member of the Jedi Council with a unique purple lightsaber, master of Vaapad fighting form, killed by Palpatine.

name: Qui-Gon Jinn
quoteHint: The ability to speak does not make you intelligent.
masterHint: Jedi Master who discovered Anakin Skywalker on Tatooine and won his freedom from Watto.

name: Darth Maul
quoteHint: At last we will reveal ourselves to the Jedi. At last we will have revenge.
masterHint: Zabrak Sith Lord with double-bladed red lightsaber who killed Qui-Gon Jinn.

name: Count Dooku
quoteHint: The Sith control everything. You just don't know it.
masterHint: Former Jedi Master turned Sith Lord who led the Separatists.

name: General Grievous
quoteHint: Your lightsabers will make a fine addition to my collection.
masterHint: Cyborg general of the Separatist Droid Army who collected lightsabers from Jedi he killed.

name: Jango Fett
quoteHint: I'm just a simple man trying to make my way in the universe.
masterHint: Mandalorian bounty hunter whose DNA was used to create the clone army.

name: Boba Fett
quoteHint: He's no good to me dead.
masterHint: Clone of a feared bounty hunter and raised as his son, he became the galaxy's most feared bounty hunter, surpassing even his father's legacy.

name: Lando Calrissian
quoteHint: Hello, what have we here?
masterHint: Smooth-talking gambler and administrator of Cloud City who betrayed and then helped save Han Solo.

name: Sheev Palpatine
quoteHint: Everything That Has Transpired Has Done So According To My Design.
masterHint: Dark Lord of the Sith who manipulated the Clone Wars to gain ultimate power.

name: Ahsoka Tano
quoteHint: If there's one thing I've learned from you, Master, it's that following direct orders isn't always the best way to solve a problem.
masterHint: Togruta Padawan of Anakin Skywalker who left the Jedi Order, survived Order 66, and became a key figure in the Rebellion.

name: Poe Dameron
quoteHint: Somehow, Palpatine returned.
masterHint: Ace pilot and commander of the Resistance's starfighter corps.

name: Finn
quoteHint: My first battle, I made a choice. I wasn't gonna kill for them.
masterHint: Former First Order stormtrooper who defected to join the Resistance.

name: Captain Phasma
quoteHint: You were always scum.
masterHint: Chrome-armored First Order captain. Defeated by Finn.

name: BB-8
quoteHint: *Affirmative beeping*
masterHint: Orange and white spherical astromech droid belonging to Poe Dameron, carried a map to Luke Skywalker.

name: Mon Mothma
quoteHint: Many Bothans died to bring us this information.
masterHint: Senator who became the first Chief of State of the New Republic, founding leader of the Rebel Alliance.

name: Wedge Antilles
quoteHint: Look at the size of that thing!
masterHint: Ace Rebel pilot who survived both Death Star battles and fought at the Battle of Hoth.

name: Jar Jar Binks
quoteHint: Oh, mooie-mooie! I love you!
masterHint: Clumsy Gungan outcast who befriended the Jedi and later became a senator, accidentally helped Palpatine gain emergency powers.

name: 4-LOM
quoteHint: Where is Han Solo? We searched your ship--he's not there. You must have stashed him somewhere.
masterHint: Protocol droid reprogrammed as a bounty hunter, partnered with Zuckuss.

name: Gial Ackbar
quoteHint: It's a trap!
masterHint: Mon Calamari admiral who commanded the Rebel fleet at the Battle of Endor.

name: Stass Allie
quoteHint: Supreme Chancellor, your guards are going to encircle you. You are not to attempt to leave that circle under any circumstances. Do you understand?
masterHint: Tholothian Jedi Master and Council member, cousin of Adi Gallia, killed during Order 66 on Saleucami.

name: Cassian Andor
quoteHint: Everything I did, I did for the Rebellion.
masterHint: Rebel intelligence officer and spy who helped steal the Death Star plans on Scarif.

name: Ponda Baba
quoteHint: *Angry grunting*
masterHint: Aqualish thug and smuggler who confronted Luke in the Mos Eisley Cantina, lost his arm to Obi-Wan's lightsaber.

name: Babu Frik
quoteHint: Hey hey!
masterHint: Tiny Anzellan droidsmith on Kijimi who helped the Resistance by bypassing C-3PO's programming restrictions.

name: Bail Organa
quoteHint: Darker days are coming, whether we act or not. If we do act, however, we can hope for a better dawn.
masterHint: Senator from Alderaan who adopted Leia, founding member of the Rebel Alliance.

name: Cad Bane
quoteHint: I'm your worst nightmare, pal.
masterHint: Ruthless Duros bounty hunter known for his wide-brimmed hat and breathing tubes, worked for the Separatists and crime syndicates.

name: Darth Bane
quoteHint: One master, one apprentice. One to embody the power, the other to crave it.
masterHint: Ancient Sith Lord who created the Rule of Two after the Sith were nearly destroyed, ensuring their survival through secrecy.

name: Ben Solo (Kylo Ren)
quoteHint: I know what I have to do, but I don't know if I have the strength to do it.
masterHint: Son of Han and Leia who fell to the dark side. He was redeemed by giving his life to save Rey.

name: Bossk
quoteHint: You can't pay enough for a bounty hunter of my expertise.
masterHint: Trandoshan bounty hunter who hunted Wookiees.

name: Ezra Bridger
quoteHint: I want to become the Jedi you see in me, the one I don't always see in myself.
masterHint: Street-smart Force-sensitive orphan who joined the Ghost crew.

name: Commander Gree (CC-1004)
quoteHint: That is a very tempting offer, Viceroy. In the meantime, I have a gift for you.
masterHint: Clone Commander who specialized in exotic terrain, served under Yoda on Kashyyyk, killed by Yoda during Order 66.

name: Commander Fox (CC-1010)
quoteHint: Can't say I blame you, Commander Tano, but all the same, you're under arrest.
masterHint: Clone Commander of the Coruscant Guard who wore distinctive red armor.

name: Commander Appo (CC-1119)
quoteHint: There's been a rebellion, sir. Don't worry. The situation is under control.
masterHint: Clone Commander who was part of the sacking of the Jedi Temple during Order 66.

name: Commander Bacara (CC-1138)
quoteHint: I hesitated for a moment when I received Order 66 because the last thing I expected was a Jedi coup. Did I feel betrayed? You bet I did.
masterHint: Clone Commander of the Galactic Marines known for his distinctive helmet, served under Ki-Adi-Mundi and executed Order 66.

name: Commander Cody (CC-2224)
quoteHint: ometimes in war, it's hard to be the one that survives.
masterHint: Clone Marshal Commander who served under Obi-Wan Kenobi.

name: Commander Wolffe (CC-3636)
quoteHint: The Emperor said the clone army has out-served its purpose and retired us. Now we spend our days just telling stories and sling for joopas.
masterHint: Clone Commander who served under Jedi Plo Koon, wore distinctive wolf-like markings, lost his eye in battle.

name: Captain Rex (CT-7567)
quoteHint: In my book, experience outranks everything.
masterHint: Clone Captain of the 501st Legion who served under Anakin Skywalker, removed his inhibitor chip, and helped the Rebellion.

name: Riyo Chuchi
quoteHint: To die for one's people is a great sacrifice. To live for one's people, an even greater sacrifice. [...] I choose to live for my people. What do you choose?
masterHint: Pantoran senator who advocated for clone rights, worked with Ahsoka Tano.

name: Rush Clovis
quoteHint: Why don't you try fighting like a man without your Jedi tricks?
masterHint: Separatist senator from Scipio who had a complicated history with Padmé Amidala and died defending the Banking Clan.

name: Salacious B. Crumb
quoteHint: *Cackling laughter*
masterHint: Served as Jabba the Hutt's court jester, known for his distinctive cackling laugh.

name: Echo (CT-1409)
quoteHint: It's not about that. It's about fighting for our brothers.
masterHint: Clone trooper thought dead at the Citadel, rescued and enhanced with cybernetics, joined Clone Force 99.

name: Commander Ponds (CT-411)
quoteHint: See if we can spare some rations. They'll be hungry.
masterHint: Clone Commander who served under Mace Windu.

name: Tup
quoteHint: Good soldiers follow orders.
masterHint: Clone trooper known as Tup whose malfunctioning inhibitor chip prematurely activated Order 66.

name: Fives (CT-5555)
quoteHint: The mission…the nightmares…they're…finally…over…
masterHint: Clone trooper who discovered the inhibitor chips, tried to warn about Order 66 but was killed before revealing the truth.

name: Jesse (CT-5597)
quoteHint: Easy with that weapon ma'am, we're here as friends.
masterHint: Clone trooper of the 501st Legion known as Jesse, wore Republic markings on his helmet, died during Order 66.

name: Kix (CT-6116)
quoteHint: When it comes to the health of the men, including you, I outrank everyone.
masterHint: Clone trooper medic known as Kix who discovered the inhibitor chip conspiracy but was captured before warning anyone.

name: Dogma (CT-6922)
quoteHint: You ever think that maybe the General knows what he is doing?
masterHint: Unquestioningly loyal clone trooper who executed his traitorous General.

name: Hevy (CT-782)
quoteHint: You may not realize it yet Fives. But you landed on the most boring post in the Outer Rim.
masterHint: Clone trooper who sacrificed himself to alert the Republic to the Separatist attack at Rishi Station.

name: Crosshair (CT-9904)
quoteHint: We don't usually work with 'regs.
masterHint: Clone sniper of Clone Force 99 known for his enhanced eyesight.

name: Biggs Darklighter
quoteHint: It'll be like old times, Luke. They'll never stop us.
masterHint: Rebel pilot from Tatooine and childhood friend of Luke Skywalker who died in the Battle of Yavin.

name: Dengar
quoteHint: Laugh it up, Khamdek. I've been disrespected my whole life—but being underestimated has its values.
masterHint: Corellian bounty hunter hired by Vader to find Han Solo, wore distinctive armor and head wrappings to hide scars.

name: Din Djarin
quoteHint: I can bring you in warm, or I can bring you in cold.
masterHint: Mandalorian bounty hunter who wielded the Darksaber.

name: Din Grogu
quoteHint: *Coos adorably*
masterHint: Young Force-sensitive member of Yoda's species who was rescued from the Jedi Temple and trained by Luke Skywalker.

name: Jan Dodonna
quoteHint: Man your ships, and may the Force be with you.
masterHint: General and lead strategist behind the Rebel Alliance attack on the first Death Star.

name: Embo
quoteHint: You're outmanned, laserblade.
masterHint: Kyuzo bounty hunter known for his wide-brimmed metal hat that doubled as a weapon and shield.

name: Galen Walton Erso
quoteHint: It's a peaceful life.
masterHint: Brilliant scientist forced to design the Death Star's weapon, secretly sabotaged it with a fatal flaw.

name: Jyn Erso
quoteHint: Rebellions are built on hope.
masterHint: Led the mission to steal the Death Star plans on Scarif.

name: Fennec Shand
quoteHint: I take it I'm worth more alive, huh?
masterHint: Elite mercenary and assassin who was saved by Boba Fett and became his partner in ruling Tatooine's underworld.

name: Kit Fisto
quoteHint: Those who have power should restrain themselves from using it.
masterHint: Nautolan Jedi Master known for his perpetual smile and aquatic combat skills, killed by Palpatine in his office.

name: Bib Fortuna
quoteHint: He's no Jedi.
masterHint: Twi'lek majordomo who served Jabba the Hutt.

name: Adi Gallia
quoteHint: Did the Brayan Elders invite you to invade their world? To transform their children into monsters?
masterHint: Tholothian Jedi Master and Council member known for her flying skills, killed by Savage Opress during the Clone Wars.

name: Saw Gerrera
quoteHint: Lies, deception!
masterHint: Partisan leader and extremist who fought against the Separatists and Empire, raised Jyn Erso after her father was taken.

name: Greedo
quoteHint: Going somewhere, Solo?
masterHint: Rodian bounty hunter who hunted Han Solo and may or may not have shot first.

name: Gregar Typho
quoteHint: We made it. I guess I was wrong. There was no danger at all. *explosion*
masterHint: Captain of Naboo's Royal Security Forces who protected Padmé Amidala, lost his left eye in service.

name: Nute Gunray
quoteHint: I want that treaty signed!
masterHint: Neimoidian Trade Federation Viceroy who invaded Naboo at Palpatine's direction, led the Separatist Council.

name: Amilyn Holdo
quoteHint: Hope is like the sun.
masterHint: Vice Admiral in the Resistance who sacrificed herself by ramming the Raddus into the First Order fleet at lightspeed.

name: Armitage Hux
quoteHint: Today is the end of the Republic!
masterHint: First Order general who commanded Starkiller Base, secretly became a spy for the Resistance before being executed.

name: IG-88B
quoteHint: I was created to succeed. I have all the capabilities and programming to engineer success. Yet…it eludes me.
masterHint: Assassin droid bounty hunter with a tall, skeletal frame, hired to find Han Solo.

name: Kanan Jarrus
quoteHint: I lost my way for a long time, but now I have a chance to change things.
masterHint: Jedi survivor of Order 66 who hid as a smuggler before training Ezra Bridger, sacrificed himself to save his crew.

name: Jek Tono Porkins
quoteHint: I can hold it!
masterHint: Rebel pilot callsign Red Six who flew in the Battle of Yavin, tragically shot down before reaching the Death Star trench.

name: K-2SO
quoteHint: I'll be there for you. Cassian said I had to.
masterHint: Imperial security droid reprogrammed by the Rebellion and became Cassian Andor's sarcastic companion.

name: Maz Kanata
quoteHint: The Force, it's calling to you. Just let it in.
masterHint: Ancient Force-sensitive pirate who ran a castle on Takodana, gave Luke's lightsaber to Finn and Rey.

name: Cal Kestis
quoteHint: I'm trash, just not approved trash.
masterHint: Jedi Padawan who survived Order 66 and went into hiding as a scrapper before being hunted by the Inquisitors.

name: Ki-Adi-Mundi
quoteHint: What about the droid attack on the Wookiees?
masterHint: Cerean Jedi Master with an enlarged cranium on the Jedi Council, killed during Order 66 on Mygeeto.

name: Plo Koon
quoteHint: I don't believe in chance, Commander. I know if we work together we will stay alive.
masterHint: Kel Dor Jedi Master who wore an antiox mask. He discovered Ahsoka Tano.

name: Eeth Koth
quoteHint: I am no Jedi. Not anymore. I am a husband. As of today, a father. And, to protect the ones I love…your doom.
masterHint: Zabrak Jedi Master on the Council known for high pain tolerance, captured by Grievous but rescued by Obi-Wan.

name: Pong Krell
quoteHint: I find it very interesting, Captain, that you are able to recognize the value of honor, for a clone.
masterHint: Jedi General who turned to the dark side, used four lightsabers, executed by his own clones on Umbara.

name: Orson Callan Krennic
quoteHint: Farming? Really? A man of your talents?
masterHint: Imperial Director of Advanced Weapons Research who oversaw Death Star construction.

name: Bo-Katan Kryze
quoteHint: Never! No outsider will ever rule Mandalore!
masterHint: Mandalorian warrior and former leader of Death Watch who later fought to reclaim Mandalore from the Empire.

name: Satine Kryze
quoteHint: War is intolerable. We have been deceived into thinking that we must be a part of it. I say the moment we committed to fighting, we already lost.
masterHint: Pacifist duchess of Mandalore and lover of Obi-Wan Kenobi.

name: Cliegg Lars
quoteHint: After I lost my leg I just couldn't ride anymore, until I heal. I don't want to give up on her, but she's been gone a month.
masterHint: Moisture farmer on Tatooine who freed and married Shmi Skywalker.

name: Shmi Skywalker Lars
quoteHint: You can't stop the change, any more than you can stop the suns from setting.
masterHint: Anakin's mother.

name: Lobot
quoteHint: The implants tell me the chances of that working were something like one in ten thousand. At best.
masterHint: Cyborg chief administrative aide to Lando Calrissian on Cloud City, enhanced with computer interface implants.

name: Mitth'raw'nuruodo
quoteHint: No one is immune from failure. All have tasted the bitterness of defeat and disappointment. A warrior must not dwell on that failure, but must learn from it and continue on.
masterHint: Brilliant Chiss Imperial Admiral who preserved the remnants of the Empire after the Emperor's death.

name: Jocasta Nu
quoteHint: If an item does not appear in our records, it does not exist.
masterHint: Elderly Jedi librarian who guarded the Jedi Archives, killed by Vader while trying to protect ancient holocrons.

name: Nien Nunb
quoteHint: It's good to be wanted.
masterHint: Smuggler and pilot who flew the Millennium Falcon with Lando during the Battle of Endor.

name: Barriss Offee
quoteHint: I've come to realize what many people in the Republic have come to realize. That the Jedi are the ones responsible for this war.
masterHint: Mirialan Jedi Padawan who framed Ahsoka Tano for terrorism before being captured.

name: Hondo Ohnaka
quoteHint: Insolence! We are pirates! We don’t even know what that means!
masterHint: Weequay pirate leader who often helped whichever side paid more during the Clone Wars.

name: Omega
quoteHint: I like you. You don't fit in around here either.
masterHint: Young female clone with pure genetic replication, became the fifth member of Clone Force 99.

name: Savage Opress
quoteHint: A brother? But all of my kin were killed.
masterHint: Zabrak Nightbrother transformed by Nightsister magic into Dooku's apprentice.

name: Owen Lars
quoteHint: Anakin is dead, Ben, and I won't let you make the same mistake twice.
masterHint: Moisture farmer who raised Luke Skywalker on Tatooine.

name: Darth Plagueis
quoteHint: *No quote here. What a... tragedy.*
masterHint: Muun Sith Lord who could manipulate midi-chlorians to create life, Palpatine's master who was killed in his sleep by... someone.

name: Unkar Plutt
quoteHint: Sixty portions!
masterHint: Crolute junk dealer on Jakku who gave Rey meager food portions for scrap.

name: Poggle the Lesser
quoteHint: I'm sending my warriors to hide in the catacombs. The Jedi must not find our designs for the Ultimate Weapon.
masterHint: Geonosian Archduke who led the droid foundries that built the Separatist army, executed by Vader on Mustafar.

name: Yarael Poof
quoteHint: Peace without justice is flawed, hollow at its core. It is the peace provided by tyranny.
masterHint: Quermian Jedi Master with elongated neck on the Council, master of mind tricks, died before the Clone Wars.

name: Boss (RC-1138)
quoteHint: There were no survivors on Devaron. Everyone was killed, including Master Halsey and his Padawan.
masterHint: Clone commando who led Delta Squad.

name: Fixer (RC-1140)
quoteHint: Respectfully, sir, it could be a trap.
masterHint: Clone commando and medic of Delta squad.

name: Sev (RC-1207)
quoteHint: I'd rather work shorthanded than have to serve with mongrels. You've seen what they're like as fleet officers. You want them as infantry?
masterHint: Clone commando and cold-blooded sniper of Delta Squad. He went missing on Kashyyyk.

name: Scorch
quoteHint: You hear that, Sev? Someone thinks I'm excellent.
masterHint: Clone commando and wise-cracking demolitions expert of Delta Squad.

name: Max Rebo
quoteHint: *Plays red ball jett organ*
masterHint: Ortolan musician and bandleader who performed in Jabba's palace and later Garsa's Sanctuary on Tatooine.

name: Revan
quoteHint: You could warn me when I do something bad. Blink once for dark side, twice for light.
masterHint: Legendary Jedi who fell to the dark side during the Mandalorian Wars, redeemed and saved the galaxy from Darth Malak's Star Forge.

name: Rey
quoteHint: And I... I am all the Jedi.
masterHint: Scavenger from Jakku who defeated the First Order.

name: Roos Tarpals
quoteHint: Weesa gonna die!
masterHint: Gungan military captain who fought in the Battle of Naboo and later sacrificed himself fighting General Grievous.

name: Sabé
quoteHint: I am Queen Amidala.
masterHint: Handmaiden and body double for Queen Amidala of Naboo, looked identical to Padmé and frequently served as her decoy.

name: Sebulba
quoteHint: You're Bantha poodoo!
masterHint: Dug podracer from Malastare known for cheating, lost the Boonta Eve Classic to young Anakin Skywalker.

name: Aayla Secura
quoteHint: I am sure you are aware that the Jedi did not initiate the Clone Wars. Our only intention is to end it and restore peace to our galaxy.
masterHint: Twi'lek Jedi Knight known for her athletic fighting style and blue lightsaber, killed during Order 66 on Felucia.

name: Bastila Shan
quoteHint: The fact that you are so strong in the Force and have had such relatively little training could have terrible consequences. For you, and for everyone around you.
masterHint: Jedi Knight with rare battle meditation ability who redeemed Revan during the Old Republic era.

name: Aurra Sing
quoteHint: A girl's gotta make a living.
masterHint: Ex-Jedi and bounty hunter with pale skin and an antenna implant, mentored Boba Fett after his father died.

name: Supreme Leader Snoke
quoteHint: There has been an awakening. Have you felt it?
masterHint: Supreme Leader of the First Order who seduced Ben Solo to the dark side, secretly a creation of Palpatine.

name: Lama Su
quoteHint: You must be anxious to inspect the units for yourself.
masterHint: Kaminoan Prime Minister who oversaw the clone army production facility on Kamino.

name: Hera Syndulla
quoteHint: If we want freedom, we must make difficult choices. I chose to leave my family, I chose to learn to fly, and then I chose to use that ability to help others in need.
masterHint: Twi'lek pilot and leader of the Ghost crew who fought against the Empire and became a general in the Rebellion.

name: Wat Tambor
quoteHint: The Techno Union army is at your disposal, Count.
masterHint: Skakoan Foreman of the Techno Union who led the Separatist occupation of Ryloth, executed on Mustafar.

name: Tarfful
quoteHint: *Wookiee roar*
masterHint: Wookiee chieftain of Kachirho who fought alongside Yoda during the Battle of Kashyyyk against the Separatists.

name: Wilhuff Tarkin
quoteHint: Fear will keep the local systems in line.
masterHint: Imperial Grand Moff who ruled through fear, commanded the Death Star's destruction of Alderaan.

name: TC-14
quoteHint: The ambassadors are Jedi Knights.
masterHint: Silver protocol droid owned by the Trade Federation who served drinks to Qui-Gon and Obi-Wan.

name: Shaak Ti
quoteHint: Don't let this be the end of the Jedi.
masterHint: Togruta Jedi Master on the Council who oversaw clone training on Kamino, died on multiple occasions depending on canon.

name: Rose Tico
quoteHint: That's how we're gonna win. Not fighting what we hate. Saving what we love.
masterHint: Resistance maintenance worker who saved Finn's life, helped disable the First Order's hyperspace tracker.

name: Trace Martez
quoteHint: Jedi or not, I consider you my friend.
masterHint: Human pilot and mechanic from Coruscant's underworld, sister to Rafa, befriended Ahsoka Tano.

name: Finis Valorum
quoteHint: The Trade Federation has blockaded the planet Naboo. The Senate must act.
masterHint: Supreme Chancellor of the Republic who was outmaneuvered by Palpatine during the Naboo crisis.

name: Asajj Ventress
quoteHint: A pleasure to finally meet a Jedi. Count Dooku speaks so highly of your Order.
masterHint: Dathomirian Nightsister trained as a Sith assassin by Count Dooku before becoming a bounty hunter seeking redemption.

name: Pre Vizsla
quoteHint: hey've given away our honor and tradition for peace. Duchess Satine and her corrupt leadership are crushing our souls, destroying our identity.
masterHint: Mandalorian warrior who led Death Watch and wielded the Darksaber, killed by Maul in combat.

name: Quinlan Vos
quoteHint: It's called psychometry, thank you very much.
masterHint: Kiffar Jedi known for his unconventional methods and ability to read object memories, survived Order 66.

name: Wicket Wystri Warrick
quoteHint: *Chattering and grumbling*
masterHint: Young Ewok scout who befriended Princess Leia and helped the Rebels defeat Imperial forces on Endor.

name: Watto
quoteHint: What, you think you're some kind of Jedi, waving your hand around like that?
masterHint: Toydarian junk dealer and slave owner on Tatooine who owned Anakin and Shmi before losing them.

name: Taun We
quoteHint: We modified their genetic structure to make them less independent.
masterHint: Female Kaminoan administrator who oversaw the clone army's creation.

name: Zam Wesell
quoteHint: It was a bounty hunter called—
masterHint: Clawdite shape-shifting assassin hired to kill Padmé, killed by Jango Fett before revealing her employer.

name: Sabine Wren
quoteHint: That might be the Mandalorian way, but it's not my way. Not anymore.
masterHint: Mandalorian warrior, explosives expert, and artist who left the Imperial Academy, joined the Ghost crew, and wielded the Darksaber.

name: Yaddle
quoteHint: Whatever lies he's told you, whatever you have done, you can make up for it now by bringing him to justice.
masterHint: Female member of Yoda's species on the Jedi Council, died confronting Count Dooku who absorbed her essence.

name: Zuckuss
quoteHint: We had worked other jobs together of course… that was when we knew when we team up, we become unstoppable!
masterHint: Gand findsman bounty hunter who relied on mystical visions, partnered with 4-LOM to hunt Han Solo.
